title: Ep. 167 - Illegal Ballot Harvesting
creator: Conservative Daily Podcast

description: On this episode, we break down the Project Veritas report on Minnesota ballot harvesting and talk about the other states Democrats will try to harvest enough ballots to put Joe Biden ahead.Want to help put a stop to this?
